Tactical World Winter 2013

DESCRIPTION:

Tactical World is the most comprehensive source for everything tactical. It serves as the source for everything tactical related to home defense, law enforcement, military and survival. The weapons and accessories include pistols, rifles, shotguns, knives, laser, lights, ammo and sights that are intended for defensive and offensive products that are available to the public.
